        A real-time computer vision system using a custom-trained YOLO model
        to detect restricted accessories such as earbuds, vape, hat, etc from live
        camera input.
      </p>

      <div class="project-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong>YOLO</strong>
          <span>Model</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong>Real-Time</strong>
          <span>Detection</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong>Custom</strong>
          <span>Dataset</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-stack">
        <h3>Technologies Used</h3>

        <div class="tech-list">
          <span>Python</span>
          <span>YOLO</span>
          <span>OpenCV</span>
          <span>Computer Vision</span>
