        <h3>Key Features</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>Custom YOLO object detection</li>
          <li>Live camera inference</li>
          <li>Restricted accessory alerts</li>
          <li>Bounding box visualization</li>
          <li>Confidence-based filtering</li>
          <li>FPS monitoring</li>
