      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Earbuds detection</li>
        <li>Confidence score display</li>
        <li>Real-time bounding boxes</li>
        <li>Single object tracking</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="panel-card">
      <img src="assets/images/yolo-2objects.png" alt="Glasses Detection">

      <h3>Alert System</h3>
      <p>
        Triggers a real-time visual warning when prohibited accessories are detected, 
        supporting workplace compliance and entry control.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Multiple object detection</li>
        <li>Visual warning overlay</li>
        <li>High-visibility alert UI</li>
        <li>Real-time FPS display</li>
      </ul>
